DD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n\t\t\t  <div class=\"product-specs\">\n\t\t\t\t  <table>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">MCN</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">21563105100</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Seal seams and permanently repair holes in tents, tarps, awnings, rainflys and camping gear like Thermarest® sleeping pads</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Treat up to up to 12’ of seams (1 oz) or repair torn outdoor fabrics with an adhesive that cures into a flexible rubber seal; also available in an 8 oz tube</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Waterproof gear with a sealant that flexes with fabric and bonds to nylon, polyester, canvas, leather and vinyl</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Apply it to repair or re-proof gear without worrying about the seal peeling or cracking; includes two applicator brushes</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Packaging may vary</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
    "short_description": "Seam Grip WP is a waterproof sealant that keeps you and your gear dry. Use it on tents, tarps, awnings and more to permanently repair torn gear. As a tent seam sealant, it works on all types of fabric including nylon, polyester, vinyl and canvas. Seal up to 12’ of tents with just 1 oz of this urethane adhesive or apply the clear glue to repair outdoor camping gear, rv awnings and even boat seats. Seam Grip is also available in an 8 oz tube. Take the handy Seam Grip WP sealant and adhesive on your next adventure, because you never know when gear will rip, leak, or fall apart.",
